name: BALTO
description: Balto memetoken is inspired by the legendary sled dog, Balto, who braved the harshest conditions to deliver life-saving medicine. Just like its namesake, Balto is here to lead the pack in the crypto world with courage and determination! Balto embodies the spirit of bravery and resilience, making it a symbol of hope and strength in the crypto community. Read more about who was BALTO in real life on https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Balto
